1
00:00:02,090 --> 00:00:04,910
Never forgive...

2
00:00:05,980 --> 00:00:08,310
Never forgive...

3
00:00:11,410 --> 00:00:16,160
I am the leader of the 7 Kin of Purgatory, Ultear!

4
00:00:16,770 --> 00:00:18,780
Bring it on, rotten daughter!

5
00:00:19,020 --> 00:00:23,120
I'm gonna teach you a lesson in your mother's place!

6
00:01:56,850 --> 00:01:57,760
Ultear!

7
00:01:58,870 --> 00:02:00,640
Don't worry about me!

8
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:03,410
Hurry and take Zeref to the evacuation area.

9
00:02:03,410 --> 00:02:04,220
Right!

10
00:02:04,220 --> 00:02:06,460
Juvia, wake up!

11
00:02:07,570 --> 00:02:09,520
Gray-sama's voice!

12
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:13,110
Ah, to be awakened by Gray-sama's voice...

13
00:02:13,690 --> 00:02:16,940
In whose sheets does Juvia awaken this morning?

14
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:18,000
Hey!

15
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:23,110
The Power of Life

16
00:02:24,710 --> 00:02:26,600
Juvia, chase after them!

17
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,020
Don't let them have Zeref!

18
00:02:28,020 --> 00:02:29,270
As you wish!

19
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:35,380
L-Leg is...

20
00:02:35,380 --> 00:02:36,480
Juvia!

21
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:38,090
Okay! Understood!

22
00:02:38,650 --> 00:02:40,550
If it's your order, Gray-sama...

23
00:02:41,550 --> 00:02:45,560
...pain means nothing!

24
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,510
I'm counting on you, Juvia.

25
00:02:58,480 --> 00:03:00,860
Ice Make Lance!

26
00:03:03,050 --> 00:03:05,620
Advance that ice's time to the future!

27
00:03:06,850 --> 00:03:08,230
Vaporize!

28
00:03:13,940 --> 00:03:15,240
Time Ark?

29
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,180
Right.

30
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:21,300
It doesn't work on humans, but I heard it's a Lost Magic that can manipulate time at will.

31
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:25,700
Gray might be fighting her at the moment...

32
00:03:25,700 --> 00:03:27,900
Ice Maker Magic wouldn't...

33
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:30,170
Aye... That's gonna be a tough match-up.

34
00:03:30,170 --> 00:03:32,510
Even Natsu was totally beat up.

35
00:03:32,510 --> 00:03:34,180
No, I wasn't!

36
00:03:34,180 --> 00:03:37,640
And besides, even if Gray ran into that cross-dressing geezer,

37
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:39,530
we don't have time to go saving him.

38
00:03:39,530 --> 00:03:40,780
Not like I wanna, either.

39
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:42,590
Why?

40
00:03:42,590 --> 00:03:46,630
If it were me, I'd beat 'em by myself, no matter what.

41
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:47,880
I wouldn't want anyone gettin' in the way.

42
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:51,260
Man, what a long friendship... Totally in sync...

43
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:52,530
It's like you can tell what the other's thinking...

44
00:03:52,530 --> 00:03:54,040
That ain't it!

45
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:57,620
Um, what about a cross-dressing geezer?

46
00:03:57,620 --> 00:04:00,750
He was a geezer when I met him on Galuna Island...

47
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,800
Man, what a shock!

48
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:06,000
Wait, wasn't the old man the disguise?

49
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:10,020
No. I definitely get a "young Master Bob" feel to the guy.

50
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:11,760
Definitely a guy!

51
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:14,720
Man, I feel sorry for Gray.

52
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:17,940
You're gonna get killed the next time you run into the guy.

53
00:04:17,940 --> 00:04:20,930
What exactly are you doing?

54
00:04:20,930 --> 00:04:22,910
A pitfall, Princess.

55
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:25,830
For when the enemy is in pursuit.

56
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:29,040
Um, not that... Why are you in a swimsuit?

57
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,440
It is raining.

58
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,620
And also, it is fanservice.

59
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:32,750
For who?

60
00:04:32,750 --> 00:04:36,310
Um, I was thinking...

61
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:39,030
Is this really the time for us to be chatting so casually?

62
00:04:39,030 --> 00:04:41,080
You're not one to talk!

63
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:43,940
Attack and defend... Two teams...

64
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,820
Guess it's time to decide.

65
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:50,170
So let's get back to business already, Lucy.

66
00:04:50,170 --> 00:04:51,430
Are you saying this is my fault?

67
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:53,160
Punishment time, yes?

68
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,580
Go back!

69
00:04:57,670 --> 00:05:01,280
Ice Make Hammer!

70
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:02,320
To the future!

71
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,520
Damn it...

72
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:09,120
Ice Magic doesn't work?

73
00:05:09,450 --> 00:05:11,410
Of course not!

74
00:05:13,460 --> 00:05:22,750
I learned Time Ark in order to kill Maker Magic wizards like my mother.

75
00:05:24,710 --> 00:05:28,220
In order... to kill Ul?!

76
00:05:49,990 --> 00:05:51,830
I hated her for so long...

77
00:05:56,290 --> 00:05:57,290
It's no use!

78
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,000
Flash Forward!

79
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:12,540
Ul cared for you!

80
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:14,540
So?

81
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:21,440
It's sad she can't show those feelings anymore!

82
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:32,700
If you can't use ice, you'll go hand-to-hand?

83
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:36,820
I'll beat you with ice.

84
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:42,080
I will beat you with Ul's magic!

85
00:06:42,470 --> 00:06:47,300
My magic, Time Ark, can manipulate the time of objects.

86
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:51,110
Move ice to its future and it vaporizes.

87
00:06:51,110 --> 00:06:53,400
Move ice to its past, and it becomes water.

88
00:06:54,250 --> 00:06:59,640
I believe in Ul's Maker Magic.

89
00:07:00,180 --> 00:07:03,030
Ice cannot defeat me.

90
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:08,740
Maker Magic won't be of any use at all!

91
00:07:28,250 --> 00:07:29,770
I...

92
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,670
I...

93
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,460
...will seal away...

94
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:33,760
...will seal away...

95
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,970
...your darkness!

96
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,970
...your darkness!

97
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:43,460
Ice isn't going to work!

98
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:48,860
I can't...

99
00:07:49,650 --> 00:07:51,030
...move its time!

100
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,280
But, how?

101
00:07:54,630 --> 00:07:58,830
You shouldn't be able to manipulate the time of living things...

102
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:02,710
Red ice... Don't tell me...

103
00:08:05,620 --> 00:08:08,130
He froze his own blood?!

104
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:11,920
Ice Blade: Seven Strike Dance!

105
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:23,510
Cutting the flesh, breaking off the bones...

106
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:26,020
What persistence...

107
00:08:27,150 --> 00:08:28,940
But...

108
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,970
But...

109
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:36,030
I cannot lose!

110
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:40,910
That pose...

111
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:44,880
Not until I've gone to the World of Great Magic!

112
00:08:45,780 --> 00:08:47,040
Ice Make:

113
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:50,550
Rozen Krone!

114
00:08:52,770 --> 00:08:57,900
It's the exact same Maker Magic as Ul!

115
00:09:00,740 --> 00:09:04,470
Maker Magic is magic that's free.

116
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:07,480
For each and every person, it takes a different form.

117
00:09:08,450 --> 00:09:11,520
Find your own form...

118
00:09:11,860 --> 00:09:15,660
If you do, then you can be as strong as anything...

119
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:23,040
I never thought... I would be able to see it again.

120
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:27,340
Ul's magic...

121
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,850
Well, I suppose so...

122
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:35,980
The same blood runs in them, after all...

123
00:09:36,970 --> 00:09:39,270
Silence!

124
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,460
Why, you...

125
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:51,790
What?

126
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:56,680
Why have you become like this? Why?!

127
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:57,530
Shut up!

128
00:09:58,250 --> 00:10:00,970
You couldn't even hope to understand!

129
00:10:04,380 --> 00:10:05,630
I was...

130
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:09,000
...abandoned by my mother!

131
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:31,070
Mom... Where are we going?

132
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:34,260
Mom?

133
00:10:39,130 --> 00:10:40,620
Mom?

134
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:46,080
I was abandoned by my mother.

135
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:52,270
Ultear-sama, we have come to pick you up.

136
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:57,560
And, the place I was sent...

137
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:01,460
Where's my mom?

138
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:03,510
Your mother has gone home.

139
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:10,130
Your mother requested that we strengthen your magic.

140
00:11:10,130 --> 00:11:11,590
Where is this?

141
00:11:11,590 --> 00:11:13,350
This is the the Bureau of Magic Development.

142
00:11:13,350 --> 00:11:17,320
It's a wonderful facility that invents a range of new magic.

143
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:21,290
Now, please go into your room.

144
00:11:21,290 --> 00:11:22,320
But...

145
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:27,630
Until your magic is strengthened, you cannot see your mother.

146
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:29,700
That's what she requested.

147
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:31,750
A change of clothes is prepared for you inside.

148
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:33,670
We will call for you soon.

149
00:11:38,710 --> 00:11:40,790
Mom...

150
00:11:40,790 --> 00:11:43,980
Why? Why did you...

151
00:11:43,980 --> 00:11:46,250
I wanna go home!

152
00:11:48,540 --> 00:11:49,930
Ultear-sama...

153
00:11:50,540 --> 00:11:51,930
It is time.

154
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,440
What?

155
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,540
What are you doing?

156
00:12:02,900 --> 00:12:04,610
This is scary!

157
00:12:04,610 --> 00:12:06,740
We are strengthening your magic.

158
00:12:06,740 --> 00:12:09,560
It may hurt a little. Please bear with us.

159
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:12,440
Think of it as for your mother's sake!

160
00:12:14,830 --> 00:12:16,900
Mom!

161
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:32,410
It is time.

162
00:12:33,450 --> 00:12:36,190
No... I won't go...

163
00:12:36,190 --> 00:12:37,400
It is time.

164
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:44,750
How goes it?

165
00:12:44,750 --> 00:12:46,580
She is quite the vessel.

166
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:49,750
We cannot even compare her to the other test subjects.

167
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:51,310
As I thought.

168
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:53,820
She is the daughter of Ul,

169
00:12:53,820 --> 00:12:57,370
who is said to be near the level of one of the 10 Great Wizard Saints...

170
00:12:57,370 --> 00:12:59,350
Increase the level by a factor of 5.

171
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:02,280
Inject the magic power for one hour.

172
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:04,030
Do not rest.

173
00:13:04,030 --> 00:13:04,910
Yes, sir.

174
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:16,570
I wanna go home...

175
00:13:16,570 --> 00:13:19,480
Hurry, come and get me...

176
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:22,420
Mom!

177
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:25,750
Mom!!

178
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:38,530
Test subject 3373 is escaping!

179
00:13:38,530 --> 00:13:41,460
We've detected an extreme rise in magic power!

180
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:43,380
What do you think?

181
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:46,590
Leave her be for now.

182
00:13:46,590 --> 00:13:51,460
Let's see what happens, daughter of Ul...

183
00:13:52,140 --> 00:13:53,260
Mom!

184
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:54,870
Mom!

185
00:13:58,120 --> 00:14:01,530
My mind and heart were in tatters

186
00:14:01,530 --> 00:14:04,940
after being subjected to magic power enhancing experiments again and again...

187
00:14:06,190 --> 00:14:09,650
I continued running, only wishing to see my mother...

188
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:16,870
But... what I saw there...

189
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:35,400
...was my mother, looking happy...

190
00:14:38,590 --> 00:14:46,780
She abandoned me, and started living a happy life with different children...

191
00:14:50,650 --> 00:14:53,070
Never forgive...

192
00:14:56,350 --> 00:15:02,120
I returned to the Bureau of Magic Development as a test subject.

193
00:15:03,370 --> 00:15:07,940
In order to get magic power, and get revenge on my mother...

194
00:15:10,390 --> 00:15:12,890
Never forgive...

195
00:15:14,860 --> 00:15:17,040
Never forgive...

196
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:20,980
What is the matter?

197
00:15:20,980 --> 00:15:21,850
Well...

198
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:26,810
The past few days, her magic power has increased abnormally rapidly.

199
00:15:26,810 --> 00:15:29,170
We think going any further may be dangerous...

200
00:15:29,170 --> 00:15:31,760
I see. Interesting.

201
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:36,980
I thought she could be a candidate for one of the five, but...

202
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:40,290
The nature of her magic is different.

203
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:43,960
Performing a Body Link with her and myself may be impossible.

204
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:47,560
Raise the level to the maximum.

205
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:51,010
But, there is danger of an explosion...

206
00:15:51,010 --> 00:15:51,670
I do not care.

207
00:15:52,570 --> 00:15:55,580
I have obtained all the magic I require.

208
00:15:55,980 --> 00:15:58,180
I have no more need for this place.

209
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:02,350
I will leave Ul's daughter as a parting gift for them.

210
00:16:05,740 --> 00:16:06,770
He disappeared...

211
00:16:06,770 --> 00:16:08,020
Hey, we've got trouble!

212
00:16:08,890 --> 00:16:10,610
The magic power is flowing in reverse!

213
00:16:10,610 --> 00:16:12,080
It's gonna explode!

214
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,240
Evacuate!

215
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:14,610
Evacuate!

216
00:16:31,290 --> 00:16:35,360
Before long, I came to learn of the existence of Zeref,

217
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:38,430
and a Dark Guild who was after him...

218
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:42,680
When Zeref is resurrected once again,

219
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:46,900
the World of Great Magic will be complete.

220
00:16:47,510 --> 00:16:49,900
World of Great Magic?

221
00:16:50,650 --> 00:16:54,460
There, all magic can be used freely...

222
00:16:54,940 --> 00:16:59,660
There is even magic that will allow you to get back happiness which was lost.

223
00:17:00,770 --> 00:17:04,660
Magic to get back lost happiness?

224
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:07,710
Time Ark.

225
00:17:07,710 --> 00:17:11,620
I will train you to use it.

226
00:17:13,180 --> 00:17:17,550
In this world, Time Ark cannot be said to be complete.

227
00:17:17,550 --> 00:17:22,820
It is an ancient Lost Magic which has been forgotten...

228
00:17:22,820 --> 00:17:28,900
But, in the World of Great Magic, Time Ark will be complete.

229
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:33,860
You can can become someone who voyages through time...

230
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:48,670
In order to do it all again...

231
00:17:48,670 --> 00:17:53,030
To change this accursed life to one of happiness...

232
00:17:56,230 --> 00:17:59,030
I will complete the World of Great Magic!

233
00:18:01,660 --> 00:18:03,140
Please, save her!

234
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:07,350
What was that voice?

235
00:18:09,410 --> 00:18:12,250
Save her, please!

236
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:14,680
Again?

237
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:19,640
Her magic power has been too great ever since she was born!

238
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:24,060
These are... my mother's memories?

239
00:18:26,730 --> 00:18:29,530
The magic power is concentrated in her tiny body,

240
00:18:29,530 --> 00:18:31,410
and her fever won't go down!

241
00:18:32,590 --> 00:18:37,000
If that's the case, there's a special facility...

242
00:18:41,370 --> 00:18:43,970
My mother's memories...

243
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:48,140
Why is something like that...

244
00:18:52,150 --> 00:18:57,670
My mother, who melted on Galuna Island and flowed into the sea...

245
00:19:00,670 --> 00:19:02,270
The sea?

246
00:19:06,100 --> 00:19:10,350
This is... inside my mother?

247
00:19:10,670 --> 00:19:12,560
Dead?

248
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:15,480
What do you mean, she's dead?

249
00:19:17,350 --> 00:19:18,750
Why?

250
00:19:19,500 --> 00:19:21,550
What in the world happened?

251
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:25,260
She's dead, and that's all.

252
00:19:26,910 --> 00:19:30,670
You were supposed to cure her!

253
00:19:31,360 --> 00:19:34,480
I heard you specialized in this...

254
00:19:34,930 --> 00:19:36,390
And yet...

255
00:19:37,290 --> 00:19:41,290
We apologize, but her magic power was just too strong.

256
00:19:41,290 --> 00:19:44,440
It was beyond our ability to cope with.

257
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:46,830
It's better for you not to see the body.

258
00:19:47,230 --> 00:19:48,520
But...

259
00:19:49,410 --> 00:19:50,710
Wait!

260
00:19:50,710 --> 00:19:53,260
Give me back my daughter!

261
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:56,060
Give Ultear back to me!

262
00:19:57,170 --> 00:19:58,570
It's different...

263
00:19:59,590 --> 00:20:04,510
It's different than what I remember...

264
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:08,930
Ice Make Gungnir!

265
00:20:34,190 --> 00:20:38,540
I heard Ul speak about you, once.

266
00:20:42,270 --> 00:20:48,730
When she was born, I felt like a light had flown into my heart...

267
00:20:49,330 --> 00:20:54,100
My dreams were filled with her bright future...

268
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:58,620
I was... so very happy.

269
00:21:00,150 --> 00:21:05,070
The infinite possible futures her tiny body held...

270
00:21:06,130 --> 00:21:08,190
The power of life...

271
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:12,590
My overflowing tears just wouldn't stop.

272
00:21:15,810 --> 00:21:21,730
I wanted to go to the World of Great Magic,

273
00:21:21,730 --> 00:21:27,270
and go back to who I was before I hated my mother...

274
00:21:28,240 --> 00:21:31,970
She was the proof of my life.

275
00:21:32,860 --> 00:21:35,050
My tear.

276
00:21:36,230 --> 00:21:38,900
Ul...tear.

277
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:47,550
I just wanted to see you once again, Mom...

278
00:21:57,620 --> 00:22:01,110
My battle is over.

279
00:22:01,110 --> 00:22:04,590
My battle ain't over yet.

280
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:08,180
You can't beat Hades.

281
00:22:08,410 --> 00:22:10,010
Doesn't seem like it.

282
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:14,930
Not gonna be possible on my own.

283
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:57,900
The weather seems like it's getting worse...

284
00:23:57,900 --> 00:24:00,970
It's just settin' the stage for a thrilling climax!

285
00:24:00,970 --> 00:24:02,380
I'm gettin' fired up!

286
00:24:02,380 --> 00:24:06,400
If it keeps raining like this, won't that halve your power, Natsu?

287
00:24:06,400 --> 00:24:07,910
Ooh, that's definitely gonna be a problem...

288
00:24:07,910 --> 00:24:10,410
Hey! You sayin' some <i>rain</i>'s gonna put out my flames?

289
00:24:10,410 --> 00:24:13,840
That delayed reaction... We don't do that style gag much.

290
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:16,530
Next time: Thunder Roar!

291
00:24:16,930 --> 00:24:20,110
And wait, it's time for the boss fight, not some comedy routine!

292
00:24:20,110 --> 00:24:22,240
So you're aware this is just a routine?

293
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:24,560
Yeah, and I wish I wasn't!

